money, and you didn't answer me.

00:04:05.020 --> 00:04:06.100
So I came back.

00:04:08.740 --> 00:04:11.059
You doing well at your
job out in the world?

00:04:11.060 --> 00:04:13.220
Running back home asking for money.

00:04:15.580 --> 00:04:18.420
But I scrimp and I save every month.

00:04:18.980 --> 00:04:20.899
