money because I had an emergency.

00:04:25.700 --> 00:04:27.900
Doesn't your money belong to the family?

00:04:29.380 --> 00:04:30.500
Look at you.

00:04:30.780 --> 00:04:32.099
From childhood to adulthood

00:04:32.100 --> 00:04:35.100
I provided you with
food, drink and education.

00:04:35.319 --> 00:04:36.959
What part of the money you give is yours?

00:04:37.006 --> 00:04:38.006
Go ahead and tell me.

00:04:39.020 --> 00:04:40.100
Let me tell you.

00:04:40.580 --> 00:04:41.580
There is no money left.

00:04:41.980 --> 00:04:43.460
Even you ask me for it, there's none.

00:04:46.780 --> 00:04:47.780
Where is there none left?

00:04:49.380 --> 00:04:50.659
Your little brother is in a relationship.

00:04:50.660 --> 00:04:52.179
They plan to get married next year.

00:04:52.180 --> 00:04:53.700
So we have to buy a house.

00:04:54.900 --> 00:04:58.620
