00:05:05.100 --> 00:05:06.300
What money could we have left?

00:05:10.820 --> 00:05:11.820
Buying a house?

00:05:11.821 --> 00:05:12.860
Yes.

00:05:13.260 --> 00:05:16.220
Every man has to buy
a house to start a family.

00:05:17.180 --> 00:05:19.340
Otherwise, where will the
children live in the future?

00:05:20.220 --> 00:05:22.060
Do you think everyone is the same as you?

00:05:23.340 --> 00:05:24.340
Tell me.

00:05:24.860 --> 00:05:26.699
I introduced you to so many people.

00:05:26.700 --> 00:05:27.819
You didn't even go to meet them.

00:05:27.820 --> 00:05:28.820
You didn't get married.

00:05:29.420 --> 00:05:34.100
