back every month for the loan.

00:05:38.740 --> 00:05:40.979
You only give back 3,000 yuan.

00:05:40.980 --> 00:05:42.780
It's not even enough to pay back the loan.

00:05:44.780 --> 00:05:45.780
How about this,

00:05:47.060 --> 00:05:49.540
save a little more each month.

00:05:50.100 --> 00:05:51.460
Get up to 4,000 yuan.

00:05:52.780 --> 00:05:56.020
If it's not enough, your father
and I will make up the rest.

00:05:57.193 --> 00:05:58.273
It's almost enough.

00:05:58.580 --> 00:05:59.580
By the way.

00:06:01.140 --> 00:06:03.580
